{"type": "article", "id": 29371, "title": "用冲浪材料打造的帽子", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-10T23:02:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160710202416K98SqJzDQsZFCiTV.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>去海边游玩自然不能少了一顶有型的遮阳帽，英国生活方式品牌 <a href=\"http://www.guapapeaks.co/\">GUAPA</a> 不仅仅满足于外观，还在制作材料上下起了功夫：在最新推出的 Surf 系列中，用来制作冲浪板的材料和帽子设计结合在了一起，取代了传统的帽檐。这种灌注了树脂的复合材料有着半透明的外观，呈现出蜂巢状的纹路，而且和冲浪板的触感无异，很有弹性。不光是帽檐的部分，Surf 系列通体防水，非常适合户外活动。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.guapapeaks.co/shop/\">购买链接</a>，售价为 39 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160710202442Cin3rHBNxDFZ7kmX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.630807\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160710202442WSRyLgzKnQTAuYit.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160710202443KXCk7m1aQMAT0Pgt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.596577\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160710202444E6c45knqGoeyuUXJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>"}